Package com.redis.foundation.io

Class DSCriteriaXML

java.lang.Object
com.redis.foundation.io.DSCriteriaXML
public class DSCriteriaXML extends Object
The DSCriteriaXML provides a collection of methods that can generate/load an XML representation of a DSCriteria object.
Since:
1.0
